description:
Will you go? God will not force you to go. He will not force you to be salt and light to the world, but what does it even mean to us? #Shorts​​​​​​​​​​​​​​ #YouTubeShorts​​​​​​​​​​​​​​ 

Listen as Pastor Ted Wilson shares insights from Thoughts from the Mount of Blessing by Adventist pioneer Ellen White: https://youtu.be/OpO-bGdxbl8?si=Kp54oWEQ1b0ctCBx.
